name: (Unofficial)FoxNewsGeekSheet
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: A new flash briefing skill from Jody Burnett at ButtonPushApps.com. This skill is a flash briefing created from the public RSS feed available from Fox News. I created this flash briefing so Alexa will read it to me on a daily basis; eliminating another email from the inbox. The flash reports on Science and Technology news as reported by Fox News on their Geek Sheet emails. Jody Burnett and ButtonPushApps are not associated with Fox News so this is deemed as an (Unofficial) Alexa skill. Enable the(Unofficial) Fox News Geek Sheet flash briefing and get informed.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
